Command Line Wrapper for Crockford's JSLint

Wrapper script adopted from MacPorts:
https://trac.macports.org/browser/trunk/dports/lang/jslint

Dependencies: Tracemonkey (might work with other JS engines too).

Install on Mac:
 port install tracemonkey +fileobject
 Save these files to your path (e.g. ~/bin):
  https://raw.github.com/salomvary/jslint-cli/master/jslint
  https://raw.github.com/douglascrockford/JSLint/master/jslint.js
 Enjoy!

Usage:
 jslint myscript.js option[=true]

Configuration: 
 Put option=value pairs into ~/.jslintrc (one per line).
 See docs for possible options:
 http://www.jslint.com/lint.html#options

Documentation:
 http://www.jslint.com/lint.html

